{"tid":1203041,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[港島郊遊]其實港島真係有唔少交通方便嘅行山路線","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:53:38.000Z","uid":225590,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04b82bef06d177d01117bab6dec6a7761e2e5f63","tid":1203041,"uid":225590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:18:34.000Z","msg":"講到港島行山<br />\n最方便而又風景靚一定係西高山<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/laughtraveleat.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/14001853/view-from-west-high-hill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Flaughtraveleat.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F14001853%2Fview-from-west-high-hill.jpg&h=635b372c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最重要係交通方便<br />\n可以由中環/金鐘搭巴士上山頂起步<br />\n講到行山<br />\n裝備當然唔少得<br />\n地圖指南針就基本啦<br />\n其他物品仲有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長袖衫褲　防蟲咬防曬，最好帶多套出汗都有替換<br />\n水同乾糧　維持體力<br />\n勞工手套　應付崎嶇山路<br />\n太陽眼鏡　太陽猛要保護雙眼<br />\n急救用品　趺親都有得用<br />\n如果要攀岩就記得要戴安全帽呀<br />\n其他各種工具就睇自己實際需要決定啦<br />\n做咩都好一定要注意自己安全</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日咁岩放假<br />\n如果唔落雨我就去行山<br />\n有興趣一齊行嘅巴絲打都可以去<br />\n到時山上面再見<br />\n雖然天文台話聽日天氣唔好<br />\n但我相信香港聽日一定會好天嘅"},{"pid":"80ab4dc4e8388ad96f27a5722be844f7a88f63d7","tid":1203041,"uid":225590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"漏咗唔記得講<br />\n怕曬嘅巴絲打可以戴埋防曬嘅蒙臉巾<br />\n而家夏天太陽咁猛<br />\n曬親塊面又紅又腫痛幾日架"},{"pid":"bbe301093201498d280849749740693d2516c9f1","tid":1203041,"uid":174789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"加油，聽日山上見"},{"pid":"8259b9a35a5e75d0039056ec255973faa2a06049","tid":1203041,"uid":225590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbe301093201498d280849749740693d2516c9f1","tid":1203041,"uid":174789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"加油，聽日山上見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n我應該一早就出發<br />\n朝早涼爽好多<br />\n一到11點就開始熱"},{"pid":"6c1f49c6110e866891aaaa360da141a4fb905d70","tid":1203041,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"天氣唔穩定，記得留意大交合天氣通知，準備好應該要嘅工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ddb2d7b315b26ba0644a4b20e2bb8e8ff27549","tid":1203041,"uid":225590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c1f49c6110e866891aaaa360da141a4fb905d70","tid":1203041,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"天氣唔穩定，記得留意大交合天氣通知，準備好應該要嘅工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"如果落雨記得帶遮"},{"pid":"c1e3030baea9cd430e5bd86619ea36bef774f335","tid":1203041,"uid":68259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"天氣熱行山補充水份固然重要<br />\n但飲完水個膠樽都好有用 行過廁所可以裝水<br />\n雖然唔飲得但可以清洗用"}]}